"I'm sorry, but Child already has body guards. They are The Peace 
Angels: Eagle Eye, Afterburner and Terradive. They are protecting 
him. Are you from the Keepers? Has Herald sent you? It's seems we are 
both weary of this alliance. Go back and teel Herlad or whoever sent 
you that in one week we are leaving the embassy to a hidden base. We 
will not be allowing anyone outside our group in, or to even know the 
whereabouts until the meeting. So their is really no point in you 
staying."
